      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/new-york-community-bancorp-is-sued-over-disclosures-stock-price-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约社区银行周二被股东提起集体诉讼，指控其隐瞒贷款组合恶化情况，导致季度意外亏损，导致股价下跌约一半。]]></description>
