      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/spacex-probed-by-california-over-sex-bias-retaliation-claims-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SpaceX 正在接受加州民权机构的调查，原因是火箭和卫星制造商兼首席执行官埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 被指控未能解决针对女性员工的普遍歧视和性骚扰问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/spacex-probed-by-california-over-sex-bias-retaliation-claims-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 18:13:33 GMT</pubDate>
